aeb9016e482c68ca7e75cc2a676d222a (03:49): Oh, okay haha.  So what do you do instead of college? Do you work already?

ef4ae3a3ef9b32eb46e33f3bc7ced673 (03:53): Tell them you want special consideration.
ef4ae3a3ef9b32eb46e33f3bc7ced673 (03:54): Attach a resume. Show up to the places asking about the status. Beg for an interview.
